<body>

  <div class="container smaller-container">
    <h1 class="text-uppercase mb-4 font-weight-bold">Practice Room Sign-up <sup><small></small></sup></h1>
    <hr>
    <h3 class="mt-4">Admin Control Panel</h3>
    
    <h4 class="mt-4 font-weight-bold">Password lookup</h4>
    <p>Please enter the information of the student and your admin password to lookup a student's password.</p>

    <form method="POST" action="password-req">
      
      <div class="form-group">
        <input type="text" required="required" id="fullName" name="fullName"/>
        <label for="input" class="control-label">Full Name</label><i class="bar"></i>
      </div>

      <div class="form-group">
        <input type="text" required="required" id="studentID" name="studentID"/>
        <label for="input" class="control-label">Student ID</label><i class="bar"></i>
      </div>

      <div class="form-group">
        <input type="password" required="required" id="password" name="password"/>
        <label for="input" class="control-label">Admin Password</label><i class="bar"></i>
      </div>

      <a class="btn btn-primary mr-2" href=".">Back</a>
      <input class="btn btn-primary mr-2" type="submit"></input>

    </form>

    <hr class="mt-5 mb-4">

    <h4 class="font-weight-bold">New announcement</h4>
    <p>Type the announcement in the following text box, this will replace the old announcement on the home page. To remove the existing announcement, leave the "New Announcement" box blank.</p>

    <form method="POST" action="announcement-req">

      <div class="form-group">
        <textarea id="announcement" id="announcement" name="announcement" style="height: 100px;" required></textarea>
        <label for="textarea" class="control-label">New Announcement</label><i class="bar"></i>
      </div>

      <div class="form-group">
        <input type="password" required="required" id="password" name="password"/>
        <label for="input" class="control-label">Admin Password</label><i class="bar"></i>
      </div>

      <a class="btn btn-primary mr-2" href=".">Back</a>
      <input class="btn btn-primary mr-2" onclick="document.getElementById('announcement').required = false" type="submit"></input>

    </form>

    <hr class="mt-5 mb-4">

    <h4 class="font-weight-bold">Disable Sign-up by Time</h4>
    <p>You can disable sign-ups for one or more specific time period(s) by checking the boxes below. This will remove all existing sign-ups during the specified time period and replace them with placeholders until the next day. You CANNOT undo this action.</p>

    <form method="POST" action="disable-req">

      <div class="checkbox mt-4">

        <label class="pure-material-checkbox mr-3">
          <input type="checkbox" name="T19001930" id="T19001930">
          <span>19:00-19:30</span>
        </label>

        <label class="pure-material-checkbox mr-3">
          <input type="checkbox" name="T19302000" id="T19302000">
          <span>19:30-20:00</span>
        </label>

        <label class="pure-material-checkbox mr-3">
          <input type="checkbox" name="T20002030" id="T20002030">
          <span>20:00-20:30</span>
        </label>

        <label class="pure-material-checkbox mr-3">
          <input type="checkbox" name="T20302100" id="T20302100">
          <span>20:30-21:00</span>
        </label>

      </div>

      <div class="form-group mt-3">
        <input type="password" required="required" id="password" name="password"/>
        <label for="input" class="control-label">Admin Password</label><i class="bar"></i>
      </div>

      <a class="btn btn-primary mr-2" href=".">Back</a>
      <input class="btn btn-primary mr-2" onclick="document.getElementById('announcement').required = false" type="submit"></input>

    </form>

    <hr class="mt-5 mb-4">

    <h4 class="font-weight-bold">Blacklist Editor</h4>
    <p>You can edit the list of students who are banned from signing up by adding their student IDs here. Student IDs need to be separated by a comma. Example: "3141, 5926, 5358". You can look up a student's ID number by searching for their email address in Teams. The new blacklist will overwrite the existing blacklist (previously added IDs appear here automatically).</p>

    <form method="POST" action="blacklist-req">

      <div class="form-group">
        <textarea id="blacklist" id="blacklist" name="blacklist" style="height: 100px" required><%= blacklist %></textarea>
        <label for="textarea" class="control-label">New Blacklist</label><i class="bar"></i>
      </div>

      <div class="form-group">
        <input type="password" required="required" id="password" name="password"/>
        <label for="input" class="control-label">Admin Password</label><i class="bar"></i>
      </div>

      <a class="btn btn-primary mr-2" href=".">Back</a>
      <input class="btn btn-primary mr-2" onclick="document.getElementById('blacklist').required = false" type="submit"></input>

    </form>

    <hr class="mt-5 mb-4">

    <h4 class="font-weight-bold">Batch Password Generation</h4>
    <p>You can look up passwords for a bunch of students at the same time. Paste all students' full names in the first text box so that each line contains one and only one student. In the second text box, paste the corresponding student IDs in an order that matches the students' names exactly. (You should be able to copy and paste the whole row from Excel or Numbers) If done correctly, the algorithm will generate a table with all the students' sign up credentials.</p>

    <p>An example of properly formatted input looks like this:</p>

    <p>Full Names</p>

    <pre>
      Jackson Finley
      Rhiann Odom
      Ayisha Neale
      Louise Alvarado
      Arlene Reeve
      Alison Orozco</pre>

    <p>Student IDs</p>

    <pre>
      2210999
      2210929
      2210839
      2210529
      2210733
      2210792</pre>

    <form method="POST" action="batch-password-req">

      <div class="form-group">
        <textarea id="fullNames" name="fullNames" style="height: 200px" required></textarea>
        <label for="textarea" class="control-label">Full Names</label><i class="bar"></i>
      </div>

      <div class="form-group">
        <textarea id="studentIDs" name="studentIDs" style="height: 200px" required></textarea>
        <label for="textarea" class="control-label">Student IDs</label><i class="bar"></i>
      </div>

      <div class="form-group">
        <input type="password" required="required" id="password" name="password"/>
        <label for="input" class="control-label">Admin Password</label><i class="bar"></i>
      </div>

      <a class="btn btn-primary mr-2" href=".">Back</a>
      <input class="btn btn-primary mr-2" onclick="document.getElementById('blacklist').required = false" type="submit"></input>

    </form>

